101.title: Google Cloud Platform Overview
101.description: This talk will give an overview of all of the GCP technologies available to developers.  It is meant to educate developers on what is available and to help them find the technology they need for their projects.  It is not meant to compare GCP with other cloud platforms.  A few quick demos may be shown depending on time.

102.title: Develop Your API Program Using the Google Cloud Platform
102.description: This talk will cover developing an API program for your company.  It will cover why and how to build an API program, the players involved, REST APIs, comparison of the Apigee platform and GCP Endpoints, a demo, building your developer community and other related technologies.
